<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Empowr App</title>
  <style>
    /* Global Styles */
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background: #f9fafb;
      color: #333;
    }
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9488, #2563eb);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    header p {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    nav {
      background: #0f172a;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }
    nav a {
      color: #f1f5f9;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    nav a:hover {
      color: #38bdf8;
    }
    section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #0d9488;
    }
    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .cta a {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #2563eb;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .cta a:hover {
      background: #1e40af;
    }
    footer {
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #f1f5f9;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Empowr App</h1>
    <p>Connecting voices, empowering change.</p>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#features">Features</a>
    <a href="#involved">Get Involved</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Empowr</h2>
    <p>Empowr is a community-driven app built for Injured Workers and Persons with Disabilities across Canada. 
    Weâ€™re creating a safe, inclusive space where people can connect, share experiences, and advocate for change.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="features">
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Community Support</h3>
        <p>Connect with others, share stories, and build solidarity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Advocacy Tools</h3>
        <p>Campaign resources to help drive change in policies and workplaces.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Educational Resources</h3>
        <p>Learn your rights, access guides, and stay informed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Podcasts & Updates</h3>
        <p>Listen to stories, insights, and conversations from the community.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="involved">
    <h2>Get Involved</h2>
    <p>Join us in making a difference! Follow Empowr on social media and be part of the movement.</p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a href="#">Follow on Facebook</a>
      <a href="#">Follow on X (Twitter)</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Email us at: <a href="mailto:contact@empowr.ca">contact@empowr.ca</a></p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Empowr App. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
